				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">My vision for this (I already posted my approval) is similar to how the Magicians in the Belgariad (in the far north thru Gar Og Nadrak) were described. 
<br />

<br />
The mage summons a demon and forces it into the form he envisions via spells. The demon is a slave to his will, but struggles constantly to escape by breaking the spell. If/when it escapes it regains its free will and may decide to try to kill the magician, just leave, open a burger stand etc. 
<br />

<br />
This is similar to charm, except that we "summon" ours from the depths of the elemental planes.<br />_________________<br />Aquilistor Portavendor
<br />
66 Magician
<br />
Ancient Dragon Slayers
<br />
Bertoxxulous
<br />

<br />
Master of the Orb, June 14 2004.
<br />
Blessed by Brell
<br />

