				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Something to add to this wonderful mix of Ideas
<br />

<br />
We should get imo 4 types of this spell, so that we may beable to decide which would be best fo the situwation at hand.
<br />

<br />
Fire:  A doorway to a firey gateway of hell spawns from thin air and a creature similar to the devils in POFire would come waltzing out awaiting our command.  Casting abilitys would be a DS of 350, hitting for about 300-450.  Casting a fire nuke of 450.
<br />

<br />
Water: A watery Gateway would splash open letting a small waterfall it the floor allowling a creature that would look similar to the crabs from POW.  Regening similar to as water pets of old (rediculasly <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile" border="0" /> ) Hitting for 400-500, higher attack. Nuke for 350.
<br />

<br />
Earth: A Golem a new design something possibly like the vine dudes but with more earth and stone in it  Portal would be opened from the ground slowly growing and building as it progresses.  Roots for 350 damage,  hits for 500-600, Hit points would obviously be the highest.
<br />

<br />
Air: A creature similar to that of Phoniex,  From above a portal opens a gust of wind and this bird swoops down and proceeds to blash stunning gusts of wind for about 200-350 damage.  swoops/claws for about 350-550.
<br />

<br />
Probably rediculas on the melee and procing damage but imagin these creatures hasted through in the flurry's plus Frenzied burn out?  <img src="images/smiles/eusa_silenced.gif" alt="Silenced" border="0" /> .
<br />

<br />
Go Go Pet groups owning VT....  <img src="images/smiles/eusa_silenced.gif" alt="Silenced" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
A Gnome mage could only dream. <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile" border="0" /><br />_________________<br />WTB PET GROUPS!</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
